org.grobid.core.annotations
Class TeiStAXParser

java.lang.Object
  org.grobid.core.annotations.TeiStAXParser

public class TeiStAXParser
extends Object

StAX parser which parses an input tei, and inserts the Citations of patents and NPL of description (<div type="description">...</div>) if found in that document.

Author:
Damien
